column16: Ryan Jackson flies out to center fielder Chris Heisey.
Bryan Anderson singles on a soft ground ball to catcher Dioner Navarro.   Matt Carpenter to 2nd.
Matt Carpenter singles on a sharp ground ball to center fielder Chris Heisey, deflected by second baseman Henry Rodriguez.   Shane Robinson scores.    Skip Schumaker to 3rd.
Skip Schumaker walks.   Shane Robinson to 2nd.
Jose Reyes singles on a sharp ground ball to left fielder Ryan Ludwick.
Justin Ruggiano flies out to right fielder Jay Bruce.
Mark Buehrle called out on strikes.
Rob Brantly walks.   Greg Dobbs to 2nd.
Greg Dobbs reaches on a fielding error by pitcher Tony Cingrani.
Fernando Martinez flies out to left fielder Xavier Paul.
Brett Wallace grounds out, first baseman Joey Votto to pitcher Tony Cingrani.
Brian Bogusevic called out on strikes.
Tyler Greene homers (10) on a fly ball to right center field.
Carlos Corporan grounds out to first baseman Joey Votto.
Matt Dominguez grounds out, shortstop Didi Gregorius to first baseman Joey Votto.
Fernando Martinez called out on strikes.
